name: Emerge: Detailed Course on Isomerism (Structural and Stereo)
description: In this course, Mohammad Kashif Alam will cover Isomerism. The course will be beneficial for aspirants who are preparing for the IIT JEE exams. The course consists of 12 sessions with a duration of 90 minutes each. The course will be delivered in Hinglish and notes will be provided in English.
